Package de.oth.hsp.hpplan.ilog

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HPPlanStatischModel
    Used to describe the HPPlan .mod file with the input and output parameters, which are passed to ilog
    HPPlanStatischRequest
    This Class is used as a request to the HPPlanStatisch model; it contains the data which is necessary for the computation of the model
    HPPlanStatischResponse
    This class is used as a container for the output values of ilog and whether the model was solvable or not
    HPPlanStatischSolvingAlgorithm
    This class is used to request the computation of a model from ilog.
    Product
    This class contains the values of a product which are necessary for the computation with ilog
    Productionsegment
    This class contains the values of a production segment which are necessary for the computation with ilog
